Description: DPO1_GEOSE - Also known as pol. Experimental evidence at protein level: Swiss-Prot protein existence level 1. In addition to polymerase activity, this DNA polymerase exhibits 5'-3' exonuclease activity. From Geobacillus stearothermophilus (Bacillus stearothermophilus).
β-lactamase; bla; confers resistance to ampicillin, carbenicillin, and related antibiotics
transcription terminator for bacteriophage T7 RNA polymerase
bidirectional E. coli tonB-P14 transcription terminator
LacZα fragment of β-galactosidase; lacZ fragment
